{"data":[{"name":"56:1","price":"Quand l’événement (le Jugement) arrivera,","arabic":"إِذَا وَقَعَتِ ٱلۡوَاقِعَةُ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4980,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:2","price":"nul ne traitera sa venue de mensonge.","arabic":"لَيۡسَ لِوَقۡعَتِهَا كَاذِبَةٌ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4981,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:3","price":"Il abaissera (les uns), il élèvera (les autres).","arabic":"خَافِضَةٞ رَّافِعَةٌ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4982,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:4","price":"Quand la terre sera secouée violemment,","arabic":"إِذَا رُجَّتِ ٱلۡأَرۡضُ رَجّٗا","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4983,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:5","price":"et les montagnes seront réduites en miettes,","arabic":"وَبُسَّتِ ٱلۡجِبَالُ بَسّٗا","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4984,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:6","price":"et qu’elles deviendront poussière éparpillée.","arabic":"فَكَانَتۡ هَبَآءٗ مُّنۢبَثّٗا","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4985,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:7","price":"alors vous serez trois catégories:","arabic":"وَكُنتُمۡ أَزۡوَٰجٗا ثَلَٰثَةٗ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4986,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:8","price":"les gens de la droite - que sont les gens de la droite ?","arabic":"فَأَصۡحَٰبُ ٱلۡمَيۡمَنَةِ مَآ أَصۡحَٰبُ ٱلۡمَيۡمَنَةِ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4987,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"[928] Les gens de la droite sont les bienheureux, qui recevront leurs livres du côté droit, et les gens de la gauche sont ceux qui recevront leurs livres du côté gauche; ce sont les malheureux.","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:9","price":"Et les gens de la gauche - que sont les gens de la gauche ?","arabic":"وَأَصۡحَٰبُ ٱلۡمَشۡـَٔمَةِ مَآ أَصۡحَٰبُ ٱلۡمَشۡـَٔمَةِ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4988,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:10","price":"Les premiers (à suivre les ordres d’Allah sur la terre) ce sont eux qui seront les premiers (dans l’au-delà)","arabic":"وَٱلسَّٰبِقُونَ ٱلسَّٰبِقُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4989,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:11","price":"Ce sont ceux-là les plus rapprochés d’Allah.","arabic":"أُوْلَٰٓئِكَ ٱلۡمُقَرَّبُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4990,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:12","price":"dans les Jardins des délices,","arabic":"فِي جَنَّٰتِ ٱلنَّعِيمِ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4991,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:13","price":"une multitude d’élus parmi les premières [générations],","arabic":"ثُلَّةٞ مِّنَ ٱلۡأَوَّلِينَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4992,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:14","price":"et un petit nombre parmi les dernières [générations],","arabic":"وَقَلِيلٞ مِّنَ ٱلۡأٓخِرِينَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4993,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:15","price":"sur des lits ornés [d’or et de pierreries],","arabic":"عَلَىٰ سُرُرٖ مَّوۡضُونَةٖ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4994,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:16","price":"s’y accoudant et se faisant face.","arabic":"مُّتَّكِـِٔينَ عَلَيۡهَا مُتَقَٰبِلِينَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4995,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:17","price":"Parmi eux circuleront des garçons éternellement jeunes,","arabic":"يَطُوفُ عَلَيۡهِمۡ وِلۡدَٰنٞ مُّخَلَّدُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4996,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:18","price":"avec des coupes, des aiguières et un verre [rempli] : d’une liqueur de source.","arabic":"بِأَكۡوَابٖ وَأَبَارِيقَ وَكَأۡسٖ مِّن مَّعِينٖ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4997,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:19","price":"Qui ne leur provoquera ni maux de tête ni étourdissement;","arabic":"لَّا يُصَدَّعُونَ عَنۡهَا وَلَا يُنزِفُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4998,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:20","price":"et des fruits de leur choix,","arabic":"وَفَٰكِهَةٖ مِّمَّا يَتَخَيَّرُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4999,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:21","price":"et toute chair d’oiseau qu’ils désireront.","arabic":"وَلَحۡمِ طَيۡرٖ مِّمَّا يَشۡتَهُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5000,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:22","price":"Et ils auront des des femmes aux grands yeux noirs,","arabic":"وَحُورٌ عِينٞ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5001,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:23","price":"pareilles à des perles en coquille.","arabic":"كَأَمۡثَٰلِ ٱللُّؤۡلُوِٕ ٱلۡمَكۡنُونِ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5002,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:24","price":"en récompense pour ce qu’ils faisaient.","arabic":"جَزَآءَۢ بِمَا كَانُواْ يَعۡمَلُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5003,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:25","price":"Ils n’y entendront ni futilité ni blasphème ;","arabic":"لَا يَسۡمَعُونَ فِيهَا لَغۡوٗا وَلَا تَأۡثِيمًا","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5004,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:26","price":"mais seulement les propos : \"Paix ! Paix ! (Salâm ! Salâm !)\"","arabic":"إِلَّا قِيلٗا سَلَٰمٗا سَلَٰمٗا","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5005,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:27","price":"Et les gens de la droite; que sont les gens de la droite ?","arabic":"وَأَصۡحَٰبُ ٱلۡيَمِينِ مَآ أَصۡحَٰبُ ٱلۡيَمِينِ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5006,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:28","price":"[Ils seront parmi] : des jujubiers sans épines,","arabic":"فِي سِدۡرٖ مَّخۡضُودٖ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5007,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:29","price":"et parmi des bananiers aux régimes bien fournis,","arabic":"وَطَلۡحٖ مَّنضُودٖ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5008,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:30","price":"dans une ombre étendue.","arabic":"وَظِلّٖ مَّمۡدُودٖ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5009,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:31","price":"[Près] d’une eau coulant continuellement,","arabic":"وَمَآءٖ مَّسۡكُوبٖ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5010,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:32","price":"et des fruits abondants.","arabic":"وَفَٰكِهَةٖ كَثِيرَةٖ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5011,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:33","price":"Ni interrompus ni défendus,","arabic":"لَّا مَقۡطُوعَةٖ وَلَا مَمۡنُوعَةٖ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5012,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:34","price":"sur des lits surélevés,","arabic":"وَفُرُشٖ مَّرۡفُوعَةٍ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5013,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:35","price":"C’est Nous qui les  avons créées à la perfection,","arabic":"إِنَّآ أَنشَأۡنَٰهُنَّ إِنشَآءٗ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5014,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"[929] Les: les houris.","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:36","price":"et Nous les avons faites vierges,","arabic":"فَجَعَلۡنَٰهُنَّ أَبۡكَارًا","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5015,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:37","price":"gracieuses, toutes de même âge,","arabic":"عُرُبًا أَتۡرَابٗا","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5016,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:38","price":"pour les gens de la droite,","arabic":"لِّأَصۡحَٰبِ ٱلۡيَمِينِ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5017,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:39","price":"une multitude d’élus parmi les premières [générations],","arabic":"ثُلَّةٞ مِّنَ ٱلۡأَوَّلِينَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5018,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:40","price":"et une multitude d’élus parmi les dernières [générations].","arabic":"وَثُلَّةٞ مِّنَ ٱلۡأٓخِرِينَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5019,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:41","price":"Et les gens de la gauche; que sont les gens de la gauche ?","arabic":"وَأَصۡحَٰبُ ٱلشِّمَالِ مَآ أَصۡحَٰبُ ٱلشِّمَالِ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5020,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:42","price":"ils seront au milieu d’un souffle brûlant et d’une eau bouillante,","arabic":"فِي سَمُومٖ وَحَمِيمٖ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5021,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:43","price":"à l’ombre d’une fumée noire.","arabic":"وَظِلّٖ مِّن يَحۡمُومٖ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5022,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:44","price":"Ni fraîche, ni douce.","arabic":"لَّا بَارِدٖ وَلَا كَرِيمٍ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5023,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:45","price":"Ils vivaient auparavant dans le luxe.","arabic":"إِنَّهُمۡ كَانُواْ قَبۡلَ ذَٰلِكَ مُتۡرَفِينَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5024,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:46","price":"Ils persistaient dans le grand péché [le polythéisme]","arabic":"وَكَانُواْ يُصِرُّونَ عَلَى ٱلۡحِنثِ ٱلۡعَظِيمِ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5025,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:47","price":"et disaient : \"Quand nous mourrons et serons poussière et ossements, serons-nous ressuscités ?","arabic":"وَكَانُواْ يَقُولُونَ أَئِذَا مِتۡنَا وَكُنَّا تُرَابٗا وَعِظَٰمًا أَءِنَّا لَمَبۡعُوثُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5026,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:48","price":"Ainsi que nos anciens ancêtres?...\"","arabic":"أَوَءَابَآؤُنَا ٱلۡأَوَّلُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5027,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:49","price":"Dis : \"En vérité les premiers et les derniers.","arabic":"قُلۡ إِنَّ ٱلۡأَوَّلِينَ وَٱلۡأٓخِرِينَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5028,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:50","price":"seront réunis pour le rendez-vous d’un jour connu.\"","arabic":"لَمَجۡمُوعُونَ إِلَىٰ مِيقَٰتِ يَوۡمٖ مَّعۡلُومٖ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5029,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:51","price":"Et puis, vous, les égarés, qui traitiez (la Résurrection) de mensonge,","arabic":"ثُمَّ إِنَّكُمۡ أَيُّهَا ٱلضَّآلُّونَ ٱلۡمُكَذِّبُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5030,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:52","price":"vous mangerez certainement d’un arbre de Zaqqûm.","arabic":"لَأٓكِلُونَ مِن شَجَرٖ مِّن زَقُّومٖ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5031,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:53","price":"Vous vous en remplirez le ventre,","arabic":"فَمَالِـُٔونَ مِنۡهَا ٱلۡبُطُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5032,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:54","price":"puis vous boirez par-dessus cela de l’eau bouillante,","arabic":"فَشَٰرِبُونَ عَلَيۡهِ مِنَ ٱلۡحَمِيمِ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5033,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:55","price":"vous en boirez comme boivent les chameaux assoiffés.","arabic":"فَشَٰرِبُونَ شُرۡبَ ٱلۡهِيمِ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5034,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:56","price":"Voilà le repas d’accueil qui leur sera servi, au jour de la Rétribution.","arabic":"هَٰذَا نُزُلُهُمۡ يَوۡمَ ٱلدِّينِ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5035,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:57","price":"C’est Nous qui vous avons créés. Pourquoi ne croiriez-vous donc pas [à la résurrection] ?","arabic":"نَحۡنُ خَلَقۡنَٰكُمۡ فَلَوۡلَا تُصَدِّقُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5036,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:58","price":"Voyez-vous donc ce que vous éjaculez :","arabic":"أَفَرَءَيۡتُم مَّا تُمۡنُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5037,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:59","price":"est-ce vous qui le créez ou [en] : Sommes-nous le Créateur ?","arabic":"ءَأَنتُمۡ تَخۡلُقُونَهُۥٓ أَمۡ نَحۡنُ ٱلۡخَٰلِقُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5038,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:60","price":"Nous avons prédéterminé la mort parmi vous. Nous ne serons point empêchés.","arabic":"نَحۡنُ قَدَّرۡنَا بَيۡنَكُمُ ٱلۡمَوۡتَ وَمَا نَحۡنُ بِمَسۡبُوقِينَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5039,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:61","price":"de vous remplacer par vos semblables, et vous faire renaître dans [un état] que vous ne savez pas.","arabic":"عَلَىٰٓ أَن نُّبَدِّلَ أَمۡثَٰلَكُمۡ وَنُنشِئَكُمۡ فِي مَا لَا تَعۡلَمُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5040,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:62","price":"Vous avez connu la première création. Ne vous rappelez-vous donc pas ?","arabic":"وَلَقَدۡ عَلِمۡتُمُ ٱلنَّشۡأَةَ ٱلۡأُولَىٰ فَلَوۡلَا تَذَكَّرُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5041,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:63","price":"Voyez-vous donc ce que vous labourez ?","arabic":"أَفَرَءَيۡتُم مَّا تَحۡرُثُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5042,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:64","price":"Est-ce vous qui le cultivez ? ou [en] sommes Nous le cultivateur ?","arabic":"ءَأَنتُمۡ تَزۡرَعُونَهُۥٓ أَمۡ نَحۡنُ ٱلزَّٰرِعُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5043,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:65","price":"Si Nous voulions, Nous le réduirions en débris. Et vous ne cesseriez pas de vous étonner et [de crier] :","arabic":"لَوۡ نَشَآءُ لَجَعَلۡنَٰهُ حُطَٰمٗا فَظَلۡتُمۡ تَفَكَّهُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5044,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:66","price":"\"Nous voilà endettés !","arabic":"إِنَّا لَمُغۡرَمُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5045,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:67","price":"Ou plutôt, exposés aux privations.\"","arabic":"بَلۡ نَحۡنُ مَحۡرُومُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5046,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:68","price":"Voyez-vous donc l’eau que vous buvez ?","arabic":"أَفَرَءَيۡتُمُ ٱلۡمَآءَ ٱلَّذِي تَشۡرَبُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5047,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:69","price":"Est-ce vous qui l’avez fait descendre du nuage ? ou [en] sommes Nous le descendeur ?","arabic":"ءَأَنتُمۡ أَنزَلۡتُمُوهُ مِنَ ٱلۡمُزۡنِ أَمۡ نَحۡنُ ٱلۡمُنزِلُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5048,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:70","price":"Si Nous voulions, Nous la rendrions salée. Pourquoi n’êtes- vous donc pas reconnaissants ?","arabic":"لَوۡ نَشَآءُ جَعَلۡنَٰهُ أُجَاجٗا فَلَوۡلَا تَشۡكُرُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5049,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:71","price":"Voyez-vous donc le feu que vous obtenez par frottement ?","arabic":"أَفَرَءَيۡتُمُ ٱلنَّارَ ٱلَّتِي تُورُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5050,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:72","price":"Est-ce vous qui avez créé son arbre ou [en] sommes Nous le Créateur ?","arabic":"ءَأَنتُمۡ أَنشَأۡتُمۡ شَجَرَتَهَآ أَمۡ نَحۡنُ ٱلۡمُنشِـُٔونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5051,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:73","price":"Nous en avons fait un rappel (de l’Enfer), et un élément utile pour ceux qui en ont besoin .","arabic":"نَحۡنُ جَعَلۡنَٰهَا تَذۡكِرَةٗ وَمَتَٰعٗا لِّلۡمُقۡوِينَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5052,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"[930] Le sens initial: pour les voyageurs campant dans le désert.","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:74","price":"Glorifie donc le nom de ton Seigneur, le Très Grand !","arabic":"فَسَبِّحۡ بِٱسۡمِ رَبِّكَ ٱلۡعَظِيمِ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5053,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:75","price":"Non !... Je jure par les positions des étoiles (dans le firmament).","arabic":"۞ فَلَآ أُقۡسِمُ بِمَوَٰقِعِ ٱلنُّجُومِ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5054,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:76","price":"Et c’est vraiment un serment solennel, si vous saviez.","arabic":"وَإِنَّهُۥ لَقَسَمٞ لَّوۡ تَعۡلَمُونَ عَظِيمٌ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5055,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:77","price":"Et c’est certainement un Coran noble,","arabic":"إِنَّهُۥ لَقُرۡءَانٞ كَرِيمٞ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5056,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:78","price":"dans un Livre bien gardé .","arabic":"فِي كِتَٰبٖ مَّكۡنُونٖ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5057,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"[931] Le Livre bien gardé: Le Livre qui est au ciel, auprès d’Allah.","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:79","price":"que seuls les purifiés touchent ;","arabic":"لَّا يَمَسُّهُۥٓ إِلَّا ٱلۡمُطَهَّرُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5058,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"[932] Les Purifiés: Ce sont les Anges qui sont seuls autorisés à le toucher. En se basant sur ce verset, le Musulman ne peut toucher la copie du Coran que s’il est en état de pureté.","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:80","price":"C’est une révélation de la part du Seigneur de l’Univers.","arabic":"تَنزِيلٞ مِّن رَّبِّ ٱلۡعَٰلَمِينَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5059,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:81","price":"Est-ce ce discours-là que vous traitez de mensonge ?","arabic":"أَفَبِهَٰذَا ٱلۡحَدِيثِ أَنتُم مُّدۡهِنُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5060,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:82","price":"Et est-ce pour vous [une façon d’être reconnaissant] à votre subsistance que de traiter (le Coran) de mensonge ?","arabic":"وَتَجۡعَلُونَ رِزۡقَكُمۡ أَنَّكُمۡ تُكَذِّبُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5061,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:83","price":"Lorsque le souffle de la vie remonte à la gorge (d’un moribond),","arabic":"فَلَوۡلَآ إِذَا بَلَغَتِ ٱلۡحُلۡقُومَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5062,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:84","price":"et qu’à ce moment-là vous regardez,","arabic":"وَأَنتُمۡ حِينَئِذٖ تَنظُرُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5063,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:85","price":"et que Nous sommes plus proche de lui que vous [qui l’entourez] mais vous ne [le] voyez point.","arabic":"وَنَحۡنُ أَقۡرَبُ إِلَيۡهِ مِنكُمۡ وَلَٰكِن لَّا تُبۡصِرُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5064,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:86","price":"Pourquoi donc, si vous croyez que vous n’avez pas de compte à rendre,","arabic":"فَلَوۡلَآ إِن كُنتُمۡ غَيۡرَ مَدِينِينَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5065,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:87","price":"ne la faites-vous pas revenir [cette âme], si vous êtes véridiques ?","arabic":"تَرۡجِعُونَهَآ إِن كُنتُمۡ صَٰدِقِينَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5066,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:88","price":"Si celui-ci est du nombre des rapprochés (d’Allah),","arabic":"فَأَمَّآ إِن كَانَ مِنَ ٱلۡمُقَرَّبِينَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5067,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:89","price":"alors (il aura) du repos, de la grâce et un Jardin de délices.","arabic":"فَرَوۡحٞ وَرَيۡحَانٞ وَجَنَّتُ نَعِيمٖ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5068,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:90","price":"Et s’il est du nombre des gens de la droite,","arabic":"وَأَمَّآ إِن كَانَ مِنۡ أَصۡحَٰبِ ٱلۡيَمِينِ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5069,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:91","price":"il sera [accueilli par ces mots] : “Paix à toi” de la part des gens de la droite.","arabic":"فَسَلَٰمٞ لَّكَ مِنۡ أَصۡحَٰبِ ٱلۡيَمِينِ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5070,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:92","price":"Et s’il est de ceux qui avaient traité de mensonge (la résurrection) et s’étaient égarés,","arabic":"وَأَمَّآ إِن كَانَ مِنَ ٱلۡمُكَذِّبِينَ ٱلضَّآلِّينَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5071,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:93","price":"alors, il sera installé dans une eau bouillante,","arabic":"فَنُزُلٞ مِّنۡ حَمِيمٖ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5072,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:94","price":"et il brûlera dans la Fournaise.","arabic":"وَتَصۡلِيَةُ جَحِيمٍ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5073,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:95","price":"C’est cela la pleine certitude.","arabic":"إِنَّ هَٰذَا لَهُوَ حَقُّ ٱلۡيَقِينِ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5074,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:96","price":"Glorifie donc le nom de ton Seigneur, le Très Grand !","arabic":"فَسَبِّحۡ بِٱسۡمِ رَبِّكَ ٱلۡعَظِيمِ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5075,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"}],"chapter":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah","Chapter Al-Waqi'ah","Waqi'ah","Surah Waqi'ah","Chapter Waqi'ah","Al Waqi'ah","Surah Al Waqi'ah","Chapter Al Waqi'ah","Surah 56","Chapter 56","The Inevitable","الواقعة"]}